<main class="wrapper h_420">
    <div class="base">
        <div class="section gray_section">
            <div class="section_inner">
                <div class="section_content text_block"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Looking%20to%20get%20started%20with%20Lisk?%20Simply%20follow%20our%205%20step%20guide%20and%20get%20involved!&amp;url=https://lisk.io/get_started" class="material-icons consensus_btn">share</a>
                    <div class="get_started_block">
                        <p>Welcome to Lisk! We are glad you found your way to us and hope that Lisk is the right platform for you! Below you'll find a short introduction video about Lisk. Further down you'll find 6 steps which we think are vital for a great Lisk experience. Please follow them carefully if this is your first time with Lisk.</p>
                        <p class="text_center"><iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Rk_0TjP1gjY?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
                        <p class="text_center text_center_mob btns_v1"><a href="https://lisk.chat/" class="btn_v2 normal_btn blue_btn" target="_blank">Join our Chat</a> <a href="https://forum.lisk.io/" class="btn_v2 normal_btn white_btn" target="_blank">Our Forum</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- <div class="section">
            <div class="video_block"><a href="http://youtube.com/" class="video_btn"><i class="fa fa-play-circle"></i></a>
                <div class="video_preview"><img src="i/get_start_video.jpg"></div>
            </div>
        </div> -->
        <div class="section white_section">
            <div class="section_inner">
                <ul class="get_started_steps">
                    <li class="get_started_unit">
                        <div class="get_started_step_title step_blue">
                            <div class="mb">
                                <div class="get_started_step_name" id="exchanges">Step 1 - Create an Account</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="get_started_step_description">
                            <p>Your start into Lisk begins with your first account. It builds the foundation for every interaction with the Lisk blockchain and Lisk services. You have two options to make an account. You can use our web login or download one of our many clients to your Windows, Mac, Linux or ARM device. </p>
                            <p><strong>Please note, if you lose access to your first passphrase you won't be able to recover your money.</strong></p>
                            <p class="btns_v1"><a href="https://login.lisk.io" class="btn_v2 normal_btn blue_btn" target="_blank">Web Login</a><a href="/download" class="btn_v2 normal_btn gray_btn">Download</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="get_started_unit">
                        <div class="get_started_step_title step_blue">
                            <div class="mb">
                                <div class="get_started_step_name">Step 2 - Get LSK</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="get_started_step_description">
                            <p>The currency that powers the Lisk network is simply called LSK. All actions taken on the network require LSK to process. You can buy LSK on nearly all major altcoin exchanges or get a small amount of free LSK on our <a href="https://faucet.lisk.io/" class="gl_link text_blue" target="_blank">faucet</a>.</p>
                            <!--<p> The current market price of 1 LISK is {{price_btc}} BTC or ${{price_usd}}.</p>-->
                            <!-- <ul class="lisk_list">
                                <li class="lisk_item"><a href="https://poloniex.com/exchange#btc_lisk" class="lisk_link" target="_blank"><div class="logo_poloniex"></div></a></li>
                                <li class="lisk_item"><a href="https://bter.com/trade/lisk_btc" class="lisk_link" target="_blank"><div class="logo_bter"></div></a></li>
                                <li class="lisk_item"><a href="#" class="lisk_link"><img src="i/logo.png"></a></li>
                            </ul> -->
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="get_started_unit">
                        <div class="get_started_step_title step_blue">
                            <div class="mb">
                                <div class="get_started_step_name">Step 3 - Configure Your Account</div>
                                <!-- <div class="get_started_step_tip">...</div> -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="get_started_step_description">
                            <p>Lisk has several advanced features that can enhance your user experience. You can start by adding a unique identity to your account for easy sending and receiving of LSK. Adding a second passphrase to increase the security and integrity of your account is also possible.</p>
                            <p><strong>Please note, if you lose access to your first or second passphrase you won't be able to recover your money.</strong></p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="get_started_unit">
                        <div class="get_started_step_title step_blue">
                            <div class="mb">
                                <div class="get_started_step_name">Step 4 - Meet our Tools</div>
                                <!-- <div class="get_started_step_tip">...</div> -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="get_started_step_description">
                            <p>We have developed various tools to make life with Lisk more comfortable. You can find them all on our Blockchain Explorer. View the richest accounts, see the latest transactions, take a look at all delegates and their statistics, watch the Lisk markets, and observe the network status. More features will be added to our Blockchain Explorer in the future.</p>
                            <p><i>Have you developed your own awesome tool and want to list it here? Contact us!</i></p> 
                            <p><a href="https://explorer.lisk.io" class="btn_v2 normal_btn blue_btn" target="_blank">Blockchain Explorer</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="get_started_unit">
                        <div class="get_started_step_title step_blue">
                            <div class="mb">
                                <div class="get_started_step_name">Step 5 - Get Involved</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="get_started_step_description">
                            <p>Lisk is a community focused experience and the users donâ€™t just control the network, they are directly responsible for its success. By getting involved in the community, users can help grow the Lisk network and improve the experience for everyone. A great place to get started is by joining our <a href="https://lisk.chat/" class="gl_link text_blue" target="_blank">Lisk Chat</a>. After that, give us a like on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Lisk-1118720888180640/" class="gl_link text_blue" target="_blank">Facebook</a>, follow us on <a href="https://twitter.com/LiskHQ" class="gl_link text_blue" target="_blank">Twitter</a>, or become a subscriber on <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Lisk" class="gl_link text_blue" target="_blank">Reddit</a>. Most importantly, keep up to date on news and developments through our <a href="https://blog.lisk.io/" class="gl_link text_blue" target="_blank">official Blog</a> on Medium.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="get_started_unit">
                        <div class="get_started_step_title step_blue">
                            <div class="mb">
                                <div class="get_started_step_name">Finished! Now you can become an App Developer.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="get_started_step_description">
                            <p>If you have already done the 5 previous steps and would like to be more involved in building the future of the Lisk network, developing your own blockchain app is a possible next step! If you already know JavaScript, you are well on your way to deploying your first app. To find out more and learn how you can get started working with our extensive APIs, read our <a href="/whitepaper" class="gl_link text_blue">White Paper</a> and <a href="{{documentation}}" class="gl_link text_blue" target="_blank">Documentation</a>.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{> footer }}
    </div>
